Type: Package
Package: RootScape
Title: Extracting Depth Resolved Metrics and Root Traits from Minirhizotron Root Scans and Flatbed Scanners 
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Johannes",
             family = "Cunow",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "johannes.cunow@gmail.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4830-1162")))
Maintainer: Johannes Cunow <johannes.cunow@gmail.com>
Description: With RootScape, analyzing root scans from minirhizotron
    tubes becomes a piece of cake. It enables the user to extract various
    root metrics and relate them to a depth distribution, analyse normal flatbed scans, or assess
    rotational biases of minirhizotron tubes. Minirhizotron scans will need to be segmented beforehand (e.g., 'RootDetector', 'RootPainter').
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/jcunow/RootScape, https://jcunow.github.io/RootScape/
BugReports: https://github.com/jcunow/RootScape/issues
